{"parse":{"title":"Regulatory Reform (Scotland) Act 2014","pageid":51984707,"revid":849118553,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox vevent\" style=\"width:22em\"><caption class=\"summary\">Regulatory Reform (Scotland) Act 2014</caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-weight: bold;\">\nAct of the Scottish Parliament</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f7/Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_United_Kingdom_%28Scotland%29.svg/140px-Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_United_Kingdom_%28Scotland%29.svg.png\" width=\"140\" height=\"135\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f7/Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_United_Kingdom_%28Scotland%29.svg/210px-Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_United_Kingdom_%28Scotland%29.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f7/Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_United_Kingdom_%28Scotland%29.svg/280px-Royal_Coat_of_Arms_of_the_United_Kingdom_%28Scotland%29.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"1550\" data-file-height=\"1500\" /><div><a href=\"/wiki/Scottish_Parliament\" title=\"Scottish Parliament\">Scottish Parliament</a></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/wiki/Long_title\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Long title\">Long title</a></th><td class=\"description\">\nAn Act of the Scottish Parliament to enable provision to be made for the purpose of promoting regulatory consistency; to make provision in relation to primary authorities; to enable provision to be made, and to make provision, as respects regulatory activities, and offences, relating to the environment; to make provision about regulatory functions relating to marine licensing, planning and street traders\u2019 licences; and for connected purposes.</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/wiki/Citation_of_United_Kingdom_legislation\" title=\"Citation of United Kingdom legislation\">Citation</a></th><td>\n2014 asp 3</td></tr><tr><th s